### GET all doctors filtered by specialization
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Doctors?$filter=specialization eq 'Cardiology'

### GET appointments for a specific date
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments?$filter=appointmentDate eq '2026-06-01'


### POST a new patient
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Akhil",
    "lastName": "Varma",
    "dateOfBirth": "1995-01-01",
    "gender": "Male",
    "bloodGroup": "O+",
    "phone": "9988776655",
    "email": "akhil@example.com",
    "registrationDate": "2026-05-31"
}

### 4. POST a new appointment
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "patientId": "f303ade3-3333-4000-c000-000000000001",
    "doctorId": "e202fce2-2222-4000-b000-000000000001",
    "appointmentDate": "2026-06-15",
    "appointmentTime": "10:00:00",
    "reason": "Routine Checkup"
}


### 5. GET patients filtered by blood group
# Note: Use 'On' because that is the key defined in your schema
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Patients?$filter=bloodGroup eq 'O-'
